title: crowley and aziraphale | somewhere only we know || good omens
author: peaches and plums
comment: And God is in the background screaming "Just kiss already." Much like us really.

Crowley loves Aziraphale so much that he spends the whole story trying to convince Aziraphale to run away with him. It is not a "silly fangirling", when you see the TV show you easy notice this, so adorable. It is impossible not to love them together.
I like how this gives off that Rom-com feels with the quotations at the bottom and the retro video filters like way to sum up their relationship. It’s so pretty.

I’m in awe of how perfectly the song matches these two.

"I knew the pathway like the back of my hand" - Crowley going to Aziraphale’s rescue becomes an ingrained habit of his
This is amazing they are perfect together great job!
